{% from "partials/icons.njk" import icon %}

{# ── INTRO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why Azalea Estates</span>
        <h2>Work that actually matters.</h2>
        <p class="lead">For over 25 years, Azalea Estates has been one of Fayette County&rsquo;s most trusted names in senior care. That reputation is built entirely by the people who work here.</p>
        <p>We&rsquo;re a small, family-owned community. That means you&rsquo;re not a number, you won&rsquo;t get lost in a corporate system, and the decisions made here are made by people who genuinely care about the outcomes. You&rsquo;ll know your residents by name, you&rsquo;ll celebrate their milestones, and on the hard days, you&rsquo;ll have a team standing beside you.</p>
        <p>If you want a career where you bring your best self to work every day and actually feel it at the end of a shift, we&rsquo;d love to meet you.</p>
        <div class="careers-intro-actions">
          <a href="#open-positions" class="btn btn--primary">View open positions</a>
          <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phoneRaw }}" class="btn btn--ghost">{{ icon('phone', 15) }} {{ site.contact.phone }}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <img src="{{ images.residentsLaughing }}"
             alt="Residents enjoying a warm moment together at Azalea Estates"
             loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

